### 變數設定（從 .env 讀取 API_GATEWAY_ID 與 AWS_REGION）
@baseUrl = https://{{$dotenv API_GATEWAY_ID}}.execute-api.{{$dotenv AWS_REGION}}.amazonaws.com/default

### ===== /api/photos =====

### 提交下載請求
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/photos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "download",
  "blog_url": "https://blog.naver.com/username/post_id"
}

### 查詢任務狀態
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/photos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "status",
  "job_id": "替換為實際的 job_id"
}

### ===== /api/whatsNew =====

### 取得新功能介紹（zh-TW）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/whatsNew
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "version": "1.4.0",
  "locale": "zh-TW"
}

